Food Fighters US - Season 2, Episode 3




This Kid's Got Moves

Troy Glass, a culinary whiz kid from Los Angeles, California, is here to put his skills to the test - and he's only 14 years old! After working in his mom's Italian restaurant for years, Troy's dream is to attend the Culinary Institute of America and become a professional chef. In fact, he plans to use the majority of his winnings to help fund his education. Does this teenage prodigy have what it takes to beat out five pro chefs?




Original Air Date: 16-Jul-2015
